title: Vojtěch Plzák
text: Vojtěch Plzák was a Czech <a href="sprint%20%28running%29">sprinter</a>. He competed in the <a href="Athletics%20at%20the%201920%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%20100%20metres">men's 100 metres</a> at the <a href="1920%20Summer%20Olympics">1920 Summer Olympics</a>.
